; display_total should not crash with non-dollar commodities (BZ#673)
;
; Using display_total in a width-constrained format string used to trigger
; an assertion failure in unistring when the account held non-dollar
; commodities.

2008/10/07  fidelity
    ass:fidelity        -1200 VLKAY @  $10.90
    ass:fidelity        1200 VLKAY @  $76.35
    inc:cap.gains

test reg --format "%10(date) %-.30(payee) %20(display_total)\n" ass:fidelity
2008/10/07 fidelity                                -1200 VLKAY
2008/10/07 fidelity                                          0
end test
